    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188480/extras/71082a3092f29273e010fa7ab0b683da.poster.avif?t=1747046008\" width=720 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188480/extras/71082a3092f29273e010fa7ab0b683da.webm?t=1747046008\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188480/extras/71082a3092f29273e010fa7ab0b683da.mp4?t=1747046008\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>潜入海岸冒险</strong><br><br>进入充满活力的 <strong>Sea Town - Fish Market Simulator</strong> 世界，体验沿海生活的刺激，建立并扩展自己的捕鱼业务。从迷人的小岛开始，探索广阔的海洋，发现独特经济体和稀有鱼类的不同岛屿。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188480/extras/23ca75ec8be85bb61e74f4777a965f01.poster.avif?t=1747046008\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188480/extras/23ca75ec8be85bb61e74f4777a965f01.webm?t=1747046008\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188480/extras/23ca75ec8be85bb61e74f4777a965f01.mp4?t=1747046008\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>驾驭动态经济</strong><br><br>在 <strong>Sea Town - Fish Market Simulator</strong> 中，经济总是在变化，鱼价每天波动。做出明智的战略决策，决定何时何地出售渔获，最大化利润。通过在不同岛屿上开设和升级市场摊位，扩展您的业务，建立横跨海洋的强大贸易网络。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188480/extras/6bdb6a91250a233abf64f4d03401cc7c.poster.avif?t=1747046008\" width=720 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188480/extras/6bdb6a91250a233abf64f4d03401cc7c.webm?t=1747046008\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188480/extras/6bdb6a91250a233abf64f4d03401cc7c.mp4?t=1747046008\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>发展并升级你的帝国</strong><br><br>升级你的船只、渔具、饵料和市场摊位，以提高效率，捕获更稀有的鱼类，并推动利润增长。你可以战略性地在不同的岛屿上开设新的市场摊位，以扩大你的影响力，最终建立自己的捕鱼帝国。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188480/extras/f54a9937b69a577c5b30cccd432236ce.poster.avif?t=1747046008\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188480/extras/f54a9937b69a577c5b30cccd432236ce.webm?t=1747046008\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188480/extras/f54a9937b69a577c5b30cccd432236ce.mp4?t=1747046008\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>体验岛屿生活</strong><br><br>不仅仅是生意—在海上一天之后，你可以在当地酒馆放松，与当地人社交，并雇佣工人帮助管理你不断扩展的企业。指挥一支船员，他们帮助捕鱼、运输货物和经营你升级的市场摊位，让你专注于扩展。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188480/extras/84b7f7955b25405143740ef31d30ad7c.poster.avif?t=1747046008\" width=720 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188480/extras/84b7f7955b25405143740ef31d30ad7c.webm?t=1747046008\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188480/extras/84b7f7955b25405143740ef31d30ad7c.mp4?t=1747046008\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>沉浸在生机勃勃的世界中</strong><br><br>进入一个动态的世界，昼夜循环影响从你捕捉到的鱼类到可用的活动。明智地规划你的日程，以最大化成功，并利用每一个机会，在这个融合策略、探索和社交互动的世界中取得胜利。<br><br>你准备好主宰市场了吗？ <strong>Sea Town - Fish Market Simulator</strong> 为您提供了一个引人入胜的体验，您将在这里建立自己的捕鱼帝国，探索广阔的海洋，成为贸易大师。",
